import {articleMapper} from "../helpers/listPublications";
import {
    ArticleTitle,
    HomeGrid,
    HomeHeader,
    HomeImage,
    HomeSection,
    HomeTitle,
    HomeWrapper
} from "../styled/Homepage.styled";

function Homepage() {
    return(
            <HomeWrapper>
                <HomeHeader>
                    <HomeTitle>La Gazette de Léon</HomeTitle>
                </HomeHeader>
                <HomeGrid>
                    <HomeSection xAxis={"1"} yAxis={"1"}>
                        <HomeImage/>
                        <ArticleTitle>Amélie Nothomb</ArticleTitle>
                    </HomeSection>
                    <HomeSection xAxis={"2"} yAxis={"1/3"}>
                        <HomeImage/>
                    </HomeSection>
                    <HomeSection xAxis={"1"} yAxis={"2"}>
                        <HomeImage/>
                    </HomeSection>
                </HomeGrid>
            </HomeWrapper>

    )
}

export default Homepage;
